title: 6 Republican 2016 hopefuls woo faithful at Texas megachurch
text: > Texas 6 Republican 2016 hopefuls woo faithful at Texas megachurch Republican Presidential candidate Rick Santorum greets attendees before the start of the a North Texas Presidential Forum hosted by Faith & Freedom Coalition and Prestonwood Baptist Church, Sunday, October 18, 2015, in Plano, Texas. (AP Photo/Brandon Wade) Set to address a presidential forum at the 40,000-member Prestonwood Baptist Church on Sunday are tea party favorites Ted Cruz, Ben Carson, Mike Huckabee and Santorum. (AP Photo/Brandon Wade)
